{"tid":732383,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"日媒狂讚比利時惡魔反擊 日本國腳：簡直是怪物","createTime":"2018-07-07T01:15:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-07T01:45:02.000Z","uid":25345,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"863342f322dd3a54243975f12a50fa7812b92765","tid":732383,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:15:52.000Z","msg":"惡魔反擊曾擊破日本<br />\n<br />\n　　比利時隊2-1擊敗巴西，成功挺進本屆世界盃四強。在上一輪與比利時交手的日本球員長友佑都不禁感歎：我們曾經也與這些怪物級別球員交過手啊！<br />\n<br />\n　　比利時人在8強依靠費南甸奴的烏龍球與迪布尼的入球，2-1擊敗森巴軍團，與法國隊會師4強。在16強，他們曾在兩球落後的情況下3-2逆轉日本，那場比賽也讓日本球員和媒體感歎這支歐洲紅魔的強大。<br />\n<br />\n　　長友佑都在比利時晉級後感歎道：「比利時太強了！我們曾與這些怪物級別的球員正面交鋒！我希望比利時隊最終奪冠！」<br />\n<br />\n　　日媒《GEKISAKA》則稱讚了迪布尼的入球――「比利時再現惡魔式反擊，繼日本隊之後，巴西隊也成為了犧牲品。素有「歐洲紅魔」之稱的比利時，攻入了擊垮「足球王國」巴西的制勝球，他們獻上了如此美妙的反擊入球。」<br />\n<br />\n　　這粒快速反擊入球與絕殺日本隊的入球如出一轍！<br />\n<br />\n　　最終，這支怪物級別的歐洲紅魔能走多遠？下一場，法國人將與他們正面交鋒，比賽時間為香港時間7月11日2時。"},{"pid":"b593e52e9eab46dd600adbe6e888265e5ca00bc4","tid":732383,"uid":51932,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:27:48.000Z","msg":"俾著大陸，輸都可以踩到人地一文不值，自己本身一定冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7295156ac0a732edf42b7facb0a82eed5e2a86d","tid":732383,"uid":48843,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:29:40.000Z","msg":"我係佢地 都想比利時拎冠軍<br />\n輸比隊冠軍隊同比利時8強出局 感覺差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"160a28606766f579ebba006220945f7a399aa44c","tid":732383,"uid":55628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:35:29.000Z","msg":"國民質素差太遠"},{"pid":"5e9d301a365290217e66df3efb82f528593b23a8","tid":732383,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7295156ac0a732edf42b7facb0a82eed5e2a86d","tid":732383,"uid":48843,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:29:40.000Z","msg":"我係佢地 都想比利時拎冠軍<br />\n輸比隊冠軍隊同比利時8強出局 感覺差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:36:12.000Z","msg":"啱 輸得心服口服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62919b1508e7add780011d3220f746a80b3201e6","tid":732383,"uid":40940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:38:41.000Z","msg":"根住比利時會輸比法國的話，日本佬又會點寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"483327af40692b4d60198951d529e2429a6cce44","tid":732383,"uid":21028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5e9d301a365290217e66df3efb82f528593b23a8","tid":732383,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7295156ac0a732edf42b7facb0a82eed5e2a86d","tid":732383,"uid":48843,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:29:40.000Z","msg":"我係佢地 都想比利時拎冠軍<br />\n輸比隊冠軍隊同比利時8強出局 感覺差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:36:12.000Z","msg":"啱 輸得心服口服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:38:53.000Z","msg":"輸畀冠軍 個名靚好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有眼睇 巴西成pat屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b230d0406e13014a86520ca44f39d2cdda99c1","tid":732383,"uid":2169,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:40:56.000Z","msg":"連登祟日撚：比利時只係識屈高 勝之不武"},{"pid":"2893e9582c5d211f39f41d8b20c6d9420929b792","tid":732383,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62919b1508e7add780011d3220f746a80b3201e6","tid":732383,"uid":40940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:38:41.000Z","msg":"根住比利時會輸比法國的話，日本佬又會點寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:41:28.000Z","msg":"超人基奧特打怪物"},{"pid":"1663283296d9ce110e8a9e0